rows.label: tlk006501_07_msg0001
rows.name:
I think Rhys and his pals will turn out
to be fine salvagers, just like you, Rex.

rows.label: tlk006501_07_msg0002
rows.name:
Trust me, I've seen a lot of salvagers in
my time, and these guys have potential.

rows.label: tlk006501_07_msg0003
rows.name:
I've only been letting them use normal
cylinders, and they still managed to
haul in some Divine Beast Quartz.

rows.label: tlk006501_07_msg0004
rows.name:
That right there shows they've got the
salvager sense.

rows.label: tlk006501_07_msg0005
rows.name:
They are always a bit worse for wear,
though, thanks to all the angry Krabble
and Lysaat they drag along with them.
